data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING $10,000 towards your CLOSING COSTS. Welcome to your new home! This move-in-ready gem is a must-see property that offers everything you've been looking for. With 2,187 square feet of living space nestled on a generous half-acre lot, this 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is sure to capture your heart.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-thought-out split floor plan that provides both privacy and functionality. The heart of this home is the updated kitchen, boasting an inviting island, sleek granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and pristine white cabinets. A pantry ensures you'll have plenty of storage space for all your culinary needs.    The warm, natural light that fills every room complements the gleaming hardwood floors, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere throughout the home. Updated fixtures and lighting add a touch of modern elegance to the space.     The screened porch is an ideal spot to enjoy the Florida weather.    Outside, you'll find mature landscaping that enhances the curb appeal of this charming property. The home is thoughtfully situated in a cul-de-sac, offering a sense of security and tranquility. The large fenced backyard provides ample space for outdoor activities and gatherings.    Please note that all measurements are estimates and should be validated by the buyer(s) to ensure accuracy.    Location-wise, this home offers easy access to major highways, including I-75, I-4, and US-301, making your daily commute a breeze. Enjoy a short 15-minute drive to the University of South Florida (USF) College, and reach downtown Tampa in just 30 minutes. Tampa International Airport is a convenient 45-minute drive away, and you're within an hour's reach of the stunning Clearwater Beach, Madeira Beach, Indian Rocks Beach, Treasure Island, and St. Petersburg beaches – all perfect for weekend getaways and beachfront relaxation.    Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this warm and inviting property your forever home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the comfort and convenience it has to offer!
